{"tid":1505291,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"衝紅燈 一問","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:34:06.000Z","uid":218714,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e298e99f0aa0c6b314e401db82ed7f7e9b5653d6","tid":1505291,"uid":218714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"原先已經扣咗5分，今日燈尾又比人影到，又準備扣5分。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇運輸署話，10分就要上堂，想請教下上堂做咩，同埋之後會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想問問，就係假若唔好彩再衝多一次，扣15分，係咪立即停三個月冇得揸，仲要重考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇類似經驗巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經知衰仔，自己唔啱，以後會小心揸車！"},{"pid":"21792654e0d53a1df11a1bef46d5613b7548a857","tid":1505291,"uid":106290,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"諗真啲有冇借架車比人揸？唔好幫人食死貓食左張罰單呀"},{"pid":"c215a704fe8467135eb7c182dd2d1564a9179bca","tid":1505291,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:34:46.000Z","msg":"唔守交通規則都唔係死罪, 但係咁撚蠢要上網問唔識google<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想睇下有無人會認真答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc5716bcbcace7eb388c923387d5211f506ab28","tid":1505291,"uid":218714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c215a704fe8467135eb7c182dd2d1564a9179bca","tid":1505291,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:34:46.000Z","msg":"唔守交通規則都唔係死罪, 但係咁撚蠢要上網問唔識google<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想睇下有無人會認真答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"對唔住巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經上過運輸處睇過<br />\n所以知道係15分會3個月，同埋10分上1日堂！<br />\n我睇下有冇類似巴打咁上下，了解下睇下實況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f357f37627471ad0d1c5e6a84597a01b9cc17011","tid":1505291,"uid":218714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"21792654e0d53a1df11a1bef46d5613b7548a857","tid":1505291,"uid":106290,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"諗真啲有冇借架車比人揸？唔好幫人食死貓食左張罰單呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"明白師兄講咩，但唔會考慮咁做，自己做自己負責"},{"pid":"d5269691005948a467f5e2c1d2de3400f07f8cf0","tid":1505291,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:38:26.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dJNfyS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a8701371f7d88ad1142cfd312f5b80f0439bfdd","tid"